'''也门内战'''是[[也门|也门]]自2014年起进行至今的[[内战|内战]]，兩個集團及其支持者各自宣稱代表葉門政府。参战一方是总统[[阿卜杜拉布·曼苏尔·哈迪|阿卜杜拉布·曼苏尔·哈迪]]领导的也门政府及其盟友[[南方运动|南方运动]]，總部設在[[亞丁|亞丁]]；另一方是[[胡塞运动|胡塞运动]]及其盟友前总统[[阿里·阿卜杜拉·萨利赫|阿里·阿卜杜拉·萨利赫]]。[[阿拉伯半島基地組織|阿拉伯半岛基地组织]]和[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]亦有限度地參與了这次内战<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/143295/asher-orkaby/houthi-who|agency=Foreign Affairs|title=Houthi Who?|first=Asher|last=Orkaby|date=2015-03-25|accessdate=2015-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150327115828/http://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/143295/asher-orkaby/houthi-who|archive-date=2015-03-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/23/world/middleeast/houthi-rebels-taiz-yemen.html?_r=1|agency=The New York Times|title=Rebels Seize Key Parts of Yemen’s Third-Largest City, Taiz|date=2015-03-22|accessdate=2015-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403041043/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/23/world/middleeast/houthi-rebels-taiz-yemen.html?_r=1|archive-date=2015-04-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="anger">{{cite news|url=http://www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/3cc4c18a-d7b3-11e4-849b-00144feab7de.html#axzz3X2WENrBM|agency=Financial Times|title=Yemen anger grows as absent president cheers attack|first=Peter|last=Salisbury|date=2015-04-07|accessdate=2015-04-11}}</ref>

基地组织阿拉伯半岛分支曾經控制了大片內陸領地，並延伸到海岸，但旋即被擊潰。隨著南方过渡委员向哈迪投誠歸順並共組聯合政府，截至2021年也门主要勢力只剩下政府軍與胡塞運動兩派<ref>{{cite web |title=革命十年之后：也门的势力分布图 |url=https://chinese.aljazeera.net/news/2021/2/11/革命十年之后也门的势力分布图 |website=ALJAZEERA |access-date=2022-05-28 |archive-date=2021-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210620065437/https://chinese.aljazeera.net/news/2021/2/11/%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E%E4%B9%9F%E9%97%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%BF%E5%8A%9B%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%9B%BE }}</ref>。

